videoSnippet.title: Major Upset in Pro Chess League - Awonder Liang Beats Fabiano Caruana
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Here are some of the biggest surprises of the day: Viswanathan Anand drew his first three games. The Minnesota Blizzard smashed the Montreal Chessbrahs. The Pittsburgh Pawngrabbers defeated the Saint Louis Arch Bishops while Awonder Liang beat Fabiano Caruana. Both Super Saturday/Sunday winners, the Armenia Eagles and the San Jose Hackers, failed to win their matches.

Read the entire article here https://www.chess.com/news/view/liang-defeats-caruana-in-thrilling-day-of-pro-chess-upsets-2439

Awonder Liang vs Fabiano Caruana
